Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:03.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不可能在的 她已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:05.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:07.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.39,0:00:10.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死是平等的 没有对谁过不过分的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:12.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经12个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是种传染病 不会有错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:21.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结城君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:39.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:49.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:54.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他比我和结城君还亲热
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:00:57.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:01.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:03.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:05.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:06.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:16.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小彻 没事吧 小彻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:28.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:31.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢透了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:33.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:37.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:46.08,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛し…愛し合うのさ もっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:46.08,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱…更加地相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:52.34,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}激しい渇きに狂いそう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:52.34,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}激烈的饥渴让我发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:02:01.53,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}目を閉じて 罪深き くちづけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:02:01.53,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闭上眼睛 罪孽深重的接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:12.29,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}お前の匂い 狂わせる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:12.29,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你的味道 令人发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:16.25,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}真夜中に目覚めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:16.25,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在半夜里睁开眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:19.28,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}狂気 愛 飲み干す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:19.28,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}把爱与疯狂喝光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:22.63,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}おいでこの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:22.63,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}过来 到我的怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:25.75,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「あっちの闇は苦いぞ」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:25.75,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「那边的黑暗是苦涩的」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:31.70,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君の惑い 揺らめく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:31.70,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你在迷惘 在动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:35.29,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて永遠になる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:35.29,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}最终将永远无法解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:38.65,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「こっちの闇は甘いぞ」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:38.65,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「这边的黑暗是甘甜的」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:44.67,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕は深く 突き刺す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:44.67,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我狠狠地刺进最深处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:47.73,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}おいでこの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:47.73,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}过来 到我的怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:51.00,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「あっちの闇は苦いよ」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:51.00,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「那边的黑暗是苦涩的哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:57.11,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君は惑い 揺らめく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:57.11,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你在迷惘 在动摇
